{
  "info": {
    "name": "100000MRR API - B2C Platform",
    "description": "B2C 在线教育平台后端 API\n\n## 认证说明\n所有需要认证的端点都需要在请求头中携带 JWT token:\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer <your_jwt_token>\n```\n\n## 角色权限\n- **USER**: 普通用户，可以浏览课程、购买课程、学习\n- **ADMIN**: 管理员，可以管理课程、用户\n- **SUPER_ADMIN**: 超级管理员，拥有所有权限",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "0.1.0"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{jwt_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "jwt_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "System",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/../health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["..", "health"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "API Info",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register New User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('jwt_token', jsonData.data.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"securepassword123\",\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/register"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('jwt_token', jsonData.data.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"securepassword123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Current User Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/me"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/refresh"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "User Management (Admin)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Users",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users?page=1&limit=10",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["users"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "page", "value": "1"},
                {"key": "limit", "value": "10"},
                {"key": "search", "value": ""},
                {"key": "role", "value": ""}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/users/:id"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update User",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Updated Name\",\n  \"role\": \"ADMIN\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/users/:id"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete User",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/users/:id"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Course Management",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List All Courses (Public)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/courses?page=1&limit=10",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["courses"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "page", "value": "1"},
                {"key": "limit", "value": "10"}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Course Details (Public)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/courses/:slug"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Enrolled Courses",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/courses/my"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Enroll in Course",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/courses/:id/enroll"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Course (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"AI 技能提升计划\",\n  \"slug\": \"ai-skills-bootcamp\",\n  \"description\": \"30 天掌握 AI 工具\",\n  \"price\": 299,\n  \"originalPrice\": 599,\n  \"thumbnail\": \"https://example.com/image.jpg\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/courses"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Course (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Updated Title\",\n  \"price\": 199,\n  \"status\": \"PUBLISHED\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/courses/:id"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
